answers.answer: The Fast Free Track Transfer initiative offers a quick and free way for refugees to travel from Ukraine to Romania, with support from UNHCR (United Nations High Commissioner for Refugees) and IOM (International Organization for Migration). This program aims to provide assistance and protection to those seeking refuge.
